          <external-xref legal-doc="usc" parsable-cite="usc/28/84">Section 84(b)</external-xref> of title 28, United States Code</cato:entity-ref>, is amended in the second sentence by inserting <quote>Bakersfield,</quote> after <quote>shall be held at</quote>. </text> </section> 
